---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const schemaJsonLd = JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "HowTo",
      "name": "How CryptoBonusList Reviews Crypto Casinos",
      "description": "Our step-by-step methodology for testing and rating crypto casinos and bonuses. Real deposits, real wagering, real withdrawal attempts.",
      "step": [
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 1,
          "name": "Registration and Deposit",
          "text": "We create a new account and deposit real cryptocurrency to test the sign-up flow, KYC requirements, and deposit processing times."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 2,
          "name": "Bonus Claim",
          "text": "We claim the bonus as a new player would, documenting any codes, opt-in requirements, or friction in the process."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 3,
          "name": "Wagering Playthrough",
          "text": "We play through wagering requirements, testing game contributions, max bet enforcement, and overall gameplay quality."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 4,
          "name": "Withdrawal Test",
          "text": "We request a withdrawal and time the entire process from request to funds arriving in our wallet."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 5,
          "name": "Support Test",
          "text": "We contact customer support with questions to evaluate response time, helpfulness, and availability."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 6,
          "name": "Terms and Licensing Audit",
          "text": "We read the full bonus terms, privacy policy, and verify the casino license with the issuing authority."
        },
        {
          "@type": "HowToStep",
          "position": 7,
          "name": "Scoring and Review",
          "text": "We assign a score based on six weighted categories and write the review with documented pros, cons, and evidence."
        }
      ],
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "CryptoBonusList",
        "url": "https://cryptobonuslist.com"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://cryptobonuslist.com" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Our Methodology" }
      ]
    }
  ]
});
---

<Layout
  title="How We Review Crypto Casinos | CryptoBonusList Methodology"
  description="Our 7-step process for testing and rating crypto casinos. Real deposits, real wagering, real withdrawals. No copy-paste, no guesswork."
  jsonld={schemaJsonLd}
>
  <article class="px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">
        HOW WE <span class="text-[#39FF14]">REVIEW</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl">
        Every casino and bonus on this site goes through the same seven-step process. No shortcuts. No copy-pasting from casino websites. No reviews without real money on the line.
      </p>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#39FF14] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#39FF14] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">REGISTRATION AND DEPOSIT</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We create a fresh account at the casino. Same process any new player goes through. We check if KYC is required upfront or delayed until withdrawal.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Then we deposit real cryptocurrency. Usually BTC, ETH, or USDT depending on what the casino accepts. We record the deposit time, transaction hash, network fees, and how long it takes for funds to credit to the account.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#8A2BE2] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#8A2BE2] text-white font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">BONUS CLAIM</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We claim the bonus exactly as a new player would. If it requires a code, we use the code. If it requires contacting support or clicking an opt-in button, we do that.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Any friction in the claiming process is documented. Hidden requirements, misleading instructions, surprise minimum deposits. If the bonus page says one thing and the terms say another, that ends up in the review.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#FAFF00] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#FAFF00] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">WAGERING PLAYTHROUGH</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We play through the wagering requirements using a mix of games. Slots, table games, live dealer. The goal is to reach the withdrawal threshold while testing the actual gameplay experience.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We verify which games count toward wagering and at what percentage. We test max bet limits by placing bets at and above the stated cap. If the casino voids a bonus for going over by one cent, players need to know that.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#39FF14] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#39FF14] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">WITHDRAWAL TEST</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          After meeting wagering requirements, we request a withdrawal. This is where many casinos show their true colors.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We document the exact withdrawal time from request to funds arriving in our wallet. KYC document requests, processing delays, pending periods, and any unexpected fees are all recorded. If a casino advertises "instant crypto withdrawals" but takes 48 hours with a manual review, that goes in the review.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#8A2BE2] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#8A2BE2] text-white font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">5</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">SUPPORT TEST</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We contact customer support through every channel the casino offers. Live chat, email, ticket system. We ask real questions about bonus terms and account verification.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Response times are timed. We check if live chat is actually 24/7 or goes offline at night. We note whether support agents know their own bonus terms or give wrong information. Unhelpful or misleading support is a red flag.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 6 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#FAFF00] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#FAFF00] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">6</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">TERMS AND LICENSING AUDIT</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We read the full bonus terms and conditions, not the marketing summary. We check for contradictions, hidden clauses, and unusually restrictive rules like maximum win caps on bonus funds.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We verify the casino license with the issuing authority. A Curacao license number should be checkable. A Malta Gaming Authority license should appear on the MGA registry. If the license info does not verify, the review reflects that.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 7 -->
      <section class="border-[3px] border-white bg-black p-8 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#39FF14] mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#39FF14] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold text-2xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center">7</span>
          <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl font-bold">SCORING AND REVIEW</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          All findings go into the scoring system. Six categories, each weighted based on how much they affect the player experience. The final rating is a weighted average, not a gut feeling.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The written review presents what we found, including screenshots and specific data points. Pros and cons are listed. The score is explained. Nothing is hidden.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Scoring Breakdown -->
      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2 mt-12">
        SCORING CATEGORIES
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">BONUS VALUE</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">20%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">Expected value given the wagering requirements. A 100% match with 60x wagering is worse than 50% with 25x. We calculate the real cost of clearing the bonus.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">WITHDRAWAL SPEED</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">20%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">From request to wallet. Crypto withdrawals should process within hours, not days. Pending periods, manual reviews, and KYC delays are factored in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">TERMS FAIRNESS</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">20%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">Are the terms clear and reasonable? Hidden wagering on free spins winnings, maximum win caps, restricted games. We flag anything that works against the player.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">LICENSING AND TRUST</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">20%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">Verified license, clean complaint history, transparent ownership. A Curacao license is not the same as a Malta or UK license. We weigh this accordingly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">GAME SELECTION</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">10%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">Provider quality, game variety, live casino options. Are popular providers present? Do games load properly? Is the lobby organized or a mess?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-[3px] border-white p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-lg font-bold text-[#39FF14]">CUSTOMER SUPPORT</h3>
            <span class="text-[#39FF14] font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm font-bold">10%</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] text-sm">Response time, knowledge of their own terms, availability. Live chat should be live. Email should get a response within 24 hours. We test both.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rating Scale -->
      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        RATING SCALE
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="bg-[#39FF14] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold px-4 py-2 min-w-30 text-center">8.0 - 10</span>
          <div>
            <span class="text-white font-[Space_Grotesk] font-bold">Excellent.</span>
            <span class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans]"> Good value, fair terms, reliable withdrawals. Worth your time and money.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="bg-[#FAFF00] text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold px-4 py-2 min-w-30 text-center">6.0 - 7.9</span>
          <div>
            <span class="text-white font-[Space_Grotesk] font-bold">Acceptable.</span>
            <span class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans]"> Some drawbacks but works in certain situations. Read the full review before committing.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="bg-[#8A2BE2] text-white font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold px-4 py-2 min-w-30 text-center">4.0 - 5.9</span>
          <div>
            <span class="text-white font-[Space_Grotesk] font-bold">Below average.</span>
            <span class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans]"> Proceed with caution. Terms are likely unfavorable or there are trust concerns.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="bg-white text-black font-[JetBrains_Mono] font-bold px-4 py-2 min-w-30 text-center">0.0 - 3.9</span>
          <div>
            <span class="text-white font-[Space_Grotesk] font-bold">Not recommended.</span>
            <span class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans]"> Poor value, problematic behavior, or serious red flags. Skip it.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Independence -->
      <h2 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 border-b-[3px] border-[#39FF14] pb-2">
        INDEPENDENCE
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We earn affiliate commissions when you sign up at casinos through our links. That is how we pay for the testing, the team, and the site itself. Full details in our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure" class="text-[#39FF14] underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2">affiliate disclosure</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Commission rates do not affect scores. A casino paying us 50% revenue share gets the same testing process and the same scoring criteria as one paying 20%. If the casino is bad, it scores badly. No exceptions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          We have declined partnerships with casinos that asked for guaranteed minimum ratings. That has happened more than once. The answer is always the same.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Updates -->
      <div class="border-[3px] border-[#FAFF00] bg-black p-6 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#FAFF00]">
        <h3 class="font-[Space_Grotesk] text-xl font-bold text-[#FAFF00] mb-2">STAYING CURRENT</h3>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Casinos change. Bonuses get updated. Withdrawal policies shift. Licenses get suspended. We re-test casinos when we get reports of changed conditions and update reviews accordingly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Every review shows its last update date. If a review is more than six months old without an update, we prioritize re-testing it. Outdated information helps no one.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <p class="text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed">
          Got questions about how we review? Think we got something wrong? <a href="/contact" class="text-[#39FF14] underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2">Tell us</a>. We would rather fix a mistake than defend it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
